00:39:02.450 --> 00:39:04.100
One of them has a v dot p.

00:39:04.100 --> 00:39:06.660
The other has minus v dot p.

00:39:06.660 --> 00:39:11.020
So because of that,
there is a net momentum

00:39:11.020 --> 00:39:14.180
