00:40:27.490 --> 00:40:29.550
Momenta in the two
directions are the same,

00:40:29.550 --> 00:40:32.190
so that contribution goes away.

00:40:32.190 --> 00:40:35.740
The first contribution
that I'm going to get

00:40:35.740 --> 00:40:47.760
