of the momentum.

00:42:44.520 --> 00:42:49.610
And they correspond to
an additional momentum

00:42:49.610 --> 00:42:53.460
of the fluid that is
proportional to the volume.

00:42:57.210 --> 00:43:02.400
It's proportional to temperature
to the fourth and something.

00:43:02.400 --> 00:43:05.990
And of course, proportional
to the velocity.

00:43:09.200 --> 00:43:14.830
Now, we are used to thinking of
the proportionality of momentum

00:43:14.830 --> 00:43:18.050
and velocity to be
some kind of a mass.

00:43:21.280 --> 00:43:24.040
If I divide that
